            <title>[CODEC-219] Don&apos;t deprecate Charsets Charset constants in favor of Java 7&apos;s java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CODEC-219</link>
                <project id="12310464" key="CODEC">Commons Codec</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Don&apos;t deprecate Charsets Charset constants in favor of Java 7&apos;s java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since we still require Java 6, we should not deprecate.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Offer better comments.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
